       You have to link the chain to an update handler above to use it ie:
         <requestHandler name="/update "class="solr.XmlUpdateRequestHandler">
           <lst name="defaults">
             <str name="update.processor">dedupe</str>
           </lst>
         </requestHandler>  
  -->
